        <mxCell id="DkJ6A0gjdahle1yMxcGl-69" value="&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;How it works :&lt;br&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;At the start each module send their own data to their neighbor.&lt;br&gt;- After that they send the last data they received&lt;br&gt;- Transmission stop after sending N-1 data&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;" vertex="1" parent="1">
